data.name: LblPathWarning.Text
data.value: The application is currently running from within your user profile folder. For Windows services, this is usually not a good idea. Unless you know what you do, use the provided installer to install it to a more permanent location or you may risk service start issues

data.name: label7.Text
data.value: Manual operation allows this application to work without installing a service. However, you must keep this application running for continued functionality. Using manual mode and the service at the same time may cause unwanted side effects
